reviewText: Love it, don't forget to laugh! The creators were mos def going for funny and silly then totally scarey. Boobs! So many random boob shots! Lol perfect B-Movie classic

I played the character Aimee in this movie (sister that worked in the adult bookstore) so of course I love it.  It was a lot of fun to make.  The scenes were shot in various locations in and around Jackson, Mississippi.
